# Your rule content

## CLI guide
### Taskmaster
taskmaster shold be runned in the Main Directory!!!

### Frontend
- Frontend is located in ./salesone-frontend
- You can run the frontend server via `pnpm run dev`
- You can add shadCn ui components via `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add {component name}` and list can be checking in https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components/
- Use ./reference as a design and component reference.

### Backend
- Python environment is using virtual environment located in ./salesone-backend/venv and can be activated via ./salesone-backend/venv/bin/activate
- Before running command always check current working directory via `pwd` to avoid directory issues
- You can run the backend server via `python manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:8003`
- After updating backend api endpoint always update api-endpoints.md located in ./salesone-backend/documents/api-endpoints.md for the developers to read

## Framework
### Frontend
- NextJS
- ShadCn: If component is needed install using `pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add COMPONENT`
- TailwindCss

### Backend
Backend uses venv in /salesone-backend. Before running a script activate the virtual environment first
- Django
- Django Rest Framework
- Postgres
- Redis
- Celery